oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Johnny Rivers at the Memorial Gym
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Metal photoplates; Middle Tennessee State University; Rivers, Johnny;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color half sheet (green and orange on yellow) announcing the Johnny Rivers "Memphis Special" starring Johnny Rivers, Chad Stewart and Jeremy Clyde, Ronnie and the Daytonas, and the Ventures at the Memorial Gym at Middle Tennessee State College on October 23. Poster features a metal photoplate of Johnny Rivers.
